[{"id":"RAW_ebdbcf7f","title":"全网最详细的 Codex 入门教程，手把手教你玩转 Vibe Coding。","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647679828&idx=1&sn=6e1c0a935c70c566ee765c02a36327a6","date":"2026-02-09 01:29:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ebdbcf7f.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"数字生命卡兹克","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":24,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_4ead9a68","title":"Yelp 如何构建 “Yelp Assistant”","link":"https://blog.bytebytego.com/p/how-yelp-built-yelp-assistant","date":"2026-02-09 16:31:03","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_4ead9a68.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"ByteByteGo Newsletter","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_401505dd","title":"3 年、1 万人，快手技术团队首次系统披露 AI 研发范式升级历程","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651274822&idx=1&sn=b4b364a2e23df2beda37e877001ea4df","date":"2026-02-09 05:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_401505dd.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ 中文","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":59,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_41ca7ce7","title":"清华刘知远团队论文：最小化结构改动，短文本到长文本丝滑升级 | ICLR 2026","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5ODEzMjIyMA==&mid=2247731450&idx=2&sn=3894cd9c6cbb1819597afd469dbf1ce3","date":"2026-02-09 10:04:00","oneSentenceSummary":"清华大学刘知远团队提出 InfLLM-V2 框架，通过最小化结构扰动的可切换稀疏注意力机制，实现了大模型从短文本到长文本的平滑、无损升级。","summary":"本文深度解析了清华大学刘知远团队入选 ICLR 2026 的研究成果 InfLLM-V2。该研究针对大模型在扩展长上下文时面临的计算开销与性能退化矛盾，提出了一种 dense-sparse 可切换注意力框架。不同于以往引入复杂新结构或可训练模块的方案，InfLLM-V2 强调“最小结构扰动”，通过复用原有 dense attention 参数并保持输出形式一致，确保了模型在“短序列预训练到长序列微调”迁移过程中的稳定性。实验表明，该方案在长文本理解、长链推理及短文本通用能力上均能匹配全注意力模型，且在推理端实现了显著的端到端加速，为工业界提供了一种低成本、高兼容性的长上下文“热升级”技术路线。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_41ca7ce7.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AI科技评论","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":20,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_48ab1cdc","title":"