 GPT 时刻真正到来","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651016172&idx=2&sn=faf9feb8f73897e4396039ad1f21bde3","date":"2026-02-09 01:16:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_12a5d7d1.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"机器之心","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":82},{"id":"RAW_ef793c6a","title":"童年的滚球兽「走进」现实？华为天才少年创业，全球首个虚实融合的实时交互视频模型来了","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651016172&idx=1&sn=ba86881c1213117489b6b5d8ddfa2778","date":"2026-02-09 01:16:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ef793c6a.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"机器之心","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":17,"score":82},{"id":"RAW_9c115a8b","title":"别再让语音机器人“答非所问”：AI Force 任务型语音对话技术总结","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247558288&idx=1&sn=1e34f7eae3421e09e8f2f78baeb5f066","date":"2026-02-10 00:32:00","oneSentenceSummary":"蚂蚁集团 AI Force 团队分享了任务型语音 Agent 的技术演进，重点介绍了自研的“衍算”推理框架，通过 Planner-Reasoner 架构解决了语音交互中的延迟、拟人化与专业化难题。","summary":"文章系统总结了 AI Force 在营销、催收等任务型语音场景下的技术实践。针对传统三段式架构（ASR-Agent-TTS）的局限，详细阐述了从第一代 SOP 流程到第二代 One-model，再到第三代“衍算”推理框架的演进过程。核心创新在于“衍算”框架，它将推理拆分为负责规划的 Planner 和负责执行的 Reasoner，并结合 One-server 架构、语义打断、极致优化的 RAG 和工具调用范式，显著降低了端到端延迟（降至 1.5s 左右），提升了指令遵循度和对话的拟人感，为企业级语音 AI 提供了成熟的工程化方案。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9c115a8b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":29,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_89098486","title":"Vercel 如何构建针对编程智能体的 AEO 追踪系统","link":"https://vercel.com/blog/how-we-built-aeo-tracking-for-coding-agents","date":"2026-02-09 13:00:00","oneSentenceSummary":"Vercel 详细介绍了其 AI 引擎优化（AEO）的技术架构，利用沙箱化 MicroVM 和归一化流水线来追踪自主编程智能体如何引用其品牌。","summary":"本文探讨了专门针对 Claude Code 和 OpenAI Codex 等编程智能体的新兴 AI 引擎优化（AEO）领域。Vercel 解释说，由于这些智能体在完整的开发环境中运行，而非简单的聊天 API，因此追踪其行为需要复杂的架构。他们的解决方案包括：使用 Vercel Sandbox 启动临时 Linux MicroVM 以实现隔离执行；通过 AI Gateway 路由 LLM 调用以实现统一的可观测性；以及实现四阶段归一化层以标准化碎片化的记录格式。关键发现显示，编程智能体在 20% 的提示词中会进行网页搜索，并将品牌推荐直接嵌入到生成的代码中，这要求从传统的 SEO 转向结构化的 AEO 策略。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_89098486.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Vercel News","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":9,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_16225284","title":"在资源受限的环境中构建 LLM：实战视角","link":"https://www.infoq.com/articles/building-llms-resource-constrained-environments/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-09 11:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_16225284.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":12,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_d05aef0d","title":"[视频播客] 与 Madelyn Olson 探讨 Valkey 的改进","link":"https://www.infoq.com/podcasts/valkey-performance-improvements/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-09 11:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_d05aef0d.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":30,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_d6825afe","title":"OpenSpec：面向 AI 编程的规范驱动开发框架","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg4MTYwMzY1Mw==&mid=2247517997&idx=1&sn=ba0a8c9bf05522b81f2b383aa2db9ac9","date":"2026-02-09 10:30:00","oneSentenceSummary":"OpenSpec 是一个面向 AI 编程的规范驱动开发框架，通过“先定规范，再写代码”的闭环流程，提升 AI 协作开发的确定性与可维护性。","summary":"本文详细介绍了 OpenSpec 框架，这是一种旨在解决 AI 辅助编程中需求歧义和流程混乱的规范驱动开发（SDD）方案。OpenSpec 核心提倡“共识规范→AI 执行→自动验证→变更归档”的闭环，通过结构化的 spec 文件锁定功能边界，为开发者与 AI 建立明确的协作契约。文章深入讲解了其三阶段工作流（创建变更、实施变更、归档变更）、目录结构设计以及 CLI 工具（openspec-cn）的使用方法。该框架不绑定特定 AI 工具，支持 Cursor、Claude Code 等主流助手，并提供了一个优化 Token 消耗的实战案例，展示了如何将模糊的需求转化为可执行、可验证的技术方案。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_d6825afe.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"奇舞精选","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":87,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_fdedec8b","title":"AI 产品用户留存仅三个月周期？对话王咏刚：“不和 AI 协作过项目，你就不是合格程序员” | 万有引力","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMDY1NDgyOQ==&mid=2247828079&idx=1&sn=93a911194a4e1f17a61661025462ecb9","date":"2026-02-09 10:29:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_fdedec8b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"CSDN","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":73,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_c4f8c7e7","title":"警钟敲响！Hinton 最新万字演讲：怒怼乔姆斯基、定义“不朽计算”、揭示人类唯一生路","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMDY1NDgyOQ==&mid=2247828079&idx=2&sn=774af098fd47c021bcfe501132287f3a","date":"2026-02-09 10:29:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c4f8c7e7.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"CSDN","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":42,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_3b94f1fc","title":"百度沧海·存储 Mantle 系统架构演进之路，SOSP'25 论文背后的故事","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5MjU0NTI5OQ==&mid=2247606328&idx=1&sn=d5787876fa3110535cca564c2c839e4f","date":"2026-02-09 10:01:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_3b94f1fc.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"百度Geek说","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":62,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_8e27286a","title":"设计模式 Trustworthy Generation：提升 RAG 信赖度","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNDEwNjk5OQ==&mid=2650542871&idx=1&sn=30f0fa05c0a2129017f6f3f19812a491","date":"2026-02-09 09:17:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_8e27286a.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"大淘宝技术","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":19,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_f72ad988","title":"当 OpenClaw 内置 LanceDB：为个人 AI 智能体打造超强长期记忆","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MzYzMjE0MQ==&mid=2247518417&idx=1&sn=27cf117f0487cff41839aaaaf4de2545","date":"2026-02-09 06:03:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f72ad988.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"字节跳动技术团队","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":20,"score":85},{"id":"